parameters: Looks like mine is one step ahead, hehe.
Yes, too bad! I caught you!
Do you think you can beat me?en(v[263]>=100)
Looks like I'm one step ahead of you, hehe.

Walking around like that, you're going to get
fucked by bandits, you know?

I wonder where the legendary Lolimon is...
Probably in a dangerous place... But I'll
definitely catch it someday.

It's nice to have the freedom to wander around
naked.

If you get caught by the bandits and can't escape,
they'll impregnate you at their hideout, and after
that, a life of slavery awaits.
My breasts are small, aren't they?

There's a shop where Lolimon can eat, it's quite
close to the Reingarnet place.
Wow... Is it okay if you see...?

Even us male warriors can handle demons to some
extent. However, most of them are just small fry.
When it comes to boss-class enemies, we can't do
anything and it's frustrating.

Aren't you cold? Oh, but this region is hot, you
know.

I have to quickly become a full-fledged loli-mon
so that I can support Marimari-sama.

You haven't been to the main guild in the city of
Rein Garnet, have you? First, please go there and
talk to the guild leader.

And if you don't join the guild, you won't be able
to take on quests or do anything else at this
branch guild.

Welcome, magical girls. This is the Traveling
Guild. How may I assist you?

If you have any questions or concerns, feel free
to ask.

The leader of this village of divine trees is a
loli monster named Alraune, and her nickname is
\C[2]Marimari\C[0]. She has a quiet personality
and spends most of her time sleeping.

She's not just sleeping, it is said that she
sleeps to stabilize the power of the village.

It seems that the delivery of the sacred white
flowers that Marimari-sama needs to consume
regularly is delayed.

It might be a good idea to ask Demetri, the close
aide, for information.

Have you started to notice the ugliness and
depravity of humans? ... Hehehe

What could possibly be hidden deep within the
beautiful Lake Paelis, I wonder?
We meet again. Here, have this today.

Well, can I have it again? I always feel a bit
guilty receiving things from you. By the way,
what's your name...

How are you doing, magical girl? Let me give you
this today.

Oh, it's you. Are you giving me something again?
Thank you, I'll do my best!

It seems like you're working hard, magical girl.
I'm cheering for you.

Are you the one who gave me an item the other day?
Thank you...

Magical girl, I'm sure you're going through a lot.
Here, please take this.
Haa... I'm not sure about this...

Have you started to notice the ugliness and
depravity of humans? ... Hehehe

I wonder what could possibly be hidden deep within
the beautiful Lake Paelis.
